    - `scan` carries: source_index, scan_index, MS_1000016_scan_start_time_unit_UO_0000031 (float32, raw Thermo minutes, NO conversion), MS_1000512_filter_string, MS_1000927_ion_injection_time_unit_UO_0000028 (float32), instrument_configuration_ref (u32 = 0-based analyzer-config index), and a `scan_windows` list (lower MS_1000501 / upper MS_1000500, unit MS:1000040) from scan LowMass/HighMass.
