   548	1. **List-of-struct repetition-level write in Parquet.Net 5.0.1.**
   549	   - Known: flat + def-level columns work (Phase 2). PARAM struct shape exists (`BuildParamField`).
   550	   - Unclear: exact rep-level array construction for `large_list<struct<...>>` in this Parquet.Net version.
