   384	
   385	### Decision 7 — spectra_metadata columns contract (what clears the error)
   386	
   387	**Source:** validator `schema/tables/spectra_metadata.columns.json`. [VERIFIED]
   388	
   389	```
   390	spectrum  : required facet; required column index:uint;
   391	            optional MS_1000511_ms_level(integer), MS_1000525_spectrum_representation(string),
   392	                     MS_1003060_number_of_data_points(uint), MS_1003059_number_of_peaks(uint)
   393	scan      : REQUIRED facet; required column source_index:uint    <-- the missing facet
   394	precursor : optional facet; if present, source_index:uint required
   395	selected_ion : optional facet; if present, source_index:uint required
   396	```
   397	
   398	`cv_inflection_spectra_metadata` (error/warn): every `${CV}_${ACC}_...` and `_unit_${CV}_${ACC}` column's
   399	CV code must be pinned (MS, UO, IMS) and the accession must resolve in the bundled OBO (else warning).
   400	Non-CV columns (`index`, `id`, `time`, `source_index`, `filter_string`, `data_processing_ref`, etc.) are skipped.
   401	**Minimum to clear the gate:** emit `scan` with `source_index:uint`. Everything else in CONTEXT is fidelity.
